{"tid":1366353,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊欣賞吓’我的書房‘喺二手書義賣場掃咗幾多貨","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:04:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33aefb34257bf5d8e49d607d84e5e1011cac8215","tid":1366353,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"尋日宣明會喺鑽石山搞既二手書義賣開波<br />\n見到老闆老豆有成7-8個紅白藍袋喺出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩兩part係尋晚放上網既<br />\n估計就係喺義賣場掃番嚟<br />\n人去睇吓掃咗幾多好書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULEOXN5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULEOXN5.png&h=30725f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHQnhN6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHQnhN6.png&h=3ef62772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2467234196653116&amp;id=777821865594366&amp;set=pcb.2467236103319592&amp;source=49&amp;refid=13&amp;__tn__=%2B%3D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2467234196653116%26id%3D777821865594366%26set%3Dpcb.2467236103319592%26source%3D49%26refid%3D13%26__tn__%3D%252B%253D&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=99af840c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2467234196653116&amp;id=777821865594366&amp;set=pcb.2467236103319592&amp;source=49&amp;refid=13&amp;__tn__=%2B%3D</a><br />\n<br />\n查實我本來尊重自由市場唔係太介意<br />\n但你哋第一日開始就咁掃（而且肯定會日日掃）<br />\n而且個量咁大<br />\n有冇諗過其他人感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba77151986db47a89e6652e48e7b15fd8c9c6a4","tid":1366353,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc46d66165471a8946cf718345bec545cd3408e5","tid":1366353,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ba77151986db47a89e6652e48e7b15fd8c9c6a4","tid":1366353,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"哩啲義賣除咗籌款<br />\n都可以俾唔起錢買書既人都可以買本書睇吓<br />\n又可以推廣閲讀風氣<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋每次義賣、每日都去將較好書掃哂<br />\n咁啲學生窮人就買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c115facb466316743acb2f148586ba47b52c79f8","tid":1366353,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc46d66165471a8946cf718345bec545cd3408e5","tid":1366353,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ba77151986db47a89e6652e48e7b15fd8c9c6a4","tid":1366353,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"哩啲義賣除咗籌款<br />\n都可以俾唔起錢買書既人都可以買本書睇吓<br />\n又可以推廣閲讀風氣<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋每次義賣、每日都去將較好書掃哂<br />\n咁啲學生窮人就買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"唯有限購<br />\n唔係就冇法子制止呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3064aee80f118b02d4fd66900a6acfbee4f7ac